string1="Land is green"
string2="water is blue"

sen1=" ".join(string1.split())
sen2=" ".join(string2.split())

sen=sen1 + sen2

print(sen)

O/p
Land is greenwater is blue

------------------------------------------------------------
we can also use using Replace

string1="Land is green"
string2="water is blue"

sen1=string1.replace("","")

sen2=string2.replace("","")

sen=sen1 + sen2

print(sen)
